      1          /**
      2           *    @file
      3           *    @brief    It implements the Zero Cross Detection Logic
      4           *
      5           *    @details  This module handles zero cross signal and generates events based on the rise, fall or no edge as
      6           *              "ZC_FALL_EDGE_EVENT", "ZC_RISE_EDGE_EVENT", "ZC_BLACKOUT_EVENT" & ZC_NO_EVENT, it provides the last event
      7           *              & current state of zero cross signal, it provides duty cycle & frequency of zero cross signal
