    194              /*
    195               *  Butterworth Lobe thresholds
    196               *
    197               *  Lobe thresholds can be customized using the ZC_LOBE_THRESHOLDS to provide an array of three elements:
    198               *  - Cycle Time
    199               *  - Positive lobe threshold
    200               *  - Negative lobe threshold
    201               *
    202               *  Array shall be ordered with cycle time ascending (from minimum to maximum)
    203               *
    204               *  Cycle time is in microseconds; use ZC_CYCLE_USEC() macro to convert a frequency to cycle time.
    205               *  Each coefficient should be provided using Q notation; use ZC_FILTER_Q() macro to convert a floating point value.
    206               */
